00:57:26.317 --> 00:57:27.152
<font color="white">Let's go.</font><font color="white"></font>

659
00:57:34.909 --> 00:57:35.910
<font color="white">What's going on?</font><font color="white"></font>

660
00:57:35.994 --> 00:57:37.620
<font color="white">Alpha Tango 312.</font><font color="white"></font>

661
00:57:37.704 --> 00:57:39.080
<font color="white">-Alpha Tango 312.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-What's going on?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

662
00:57:39.664 --> 00:57:42.542
<font color="white">-Alpha Tango 312. We have a situation.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-What do you think? We have a situation.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

663
00:57:43.376 --> 00:57:45.920
<font color="white">Intruder alert. We have a situation.</font><font color="white"></font>

664
00:57:46.004 --> 00:57:46.838
<font color="white">-Possible intruder.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Where are you?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

665
00:57:46.921 --> 00:57:48.923
<font color="white">The top-level security building</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">is experiencing a blackout.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

666
00:57:49.007 --> 00:57:50.842
<font color="white">-Restore power now.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-We'll begin the recovery process.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

667
00:57:50.925 --> 00:57:52.010
<font color="white">Send the recovery team.</font><font color="white"></font>

668
00:57:59.309 --> 00:58:00.268
<font color="white">Be careful.</font><font color="white"></font>

669
00:58:03.938 --> 00:58:05.023
<font color="white">Hold on.</font><font color="white"></font>

670
00:58:05.106 --> 00:58:06.149
<font color="white">It's here.</font><font color="white"></font>

671
00:58:09.986 --> 00:58:11.488
<font color="white">I'll catch you from down there.</font><font color="white"></font>

672
00:58:13.865 --> 00:58:14.699
<font color="white">Uncle.</font><font color="white"></font>

673
00:58:17.952 --> 00:58:18.786
<font color="white">Come down.</font><font color="white"></font>

674
00:58:19.412 --> 00:58:20.538
<font color="white">I'll catch you.</font><font color="white"></font>

675
00:58:21.498 --> 00:58:24.209
<font color="white">It's okay. Just trust me.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">and lower your legs first.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

676
00:58:25.126 --> 00:58:26.002
<font color="white">That's it.</font><font color="white"></font>

677
00:58:26.669 --> 00:58:27.879
<font color="white">Slowly.</font><font color="white"></font>

678
00:58:28.505 --> 00:58:29.756
<font color="white">That's it. I got you.</font><font color="white"></font>

679
00:58:29.839 --> 00:58:31.674
<font color="white">It's okay. One. two…</font><font color="white"></font>

680
00:58:41.017 --> 00:58:41.976
<font color="white">ZONE C BUNKER</font><font color="white"></font>

681
00:58:43.353 --> 00:58:44.771
<font color="white">ACCESS DENIED</font><font color="white"></font>

682
00:58:49.651 --> 00:58:50.485
<font color="white">What is it?</font><font color="white"></font>

683
00:58:52.987 --> 00:58:54.072
<font color="white">Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

684
00:58:55.073 --> 00:58:56.199
<font color="white">How good is your acting?</font><font color="white"></font>

685
00:59:06.251 --> 00:59:07.085
<font color="white">Hold it open.</font><font color="white"></font>

686
00:59:12.131 --> 00:59:13.132
<font color="white">Let's go.</font><font color="white"></font>

687
00:59:23.268 --> 00:59:24.102
<font color="white">Let's go.</font><font color="white"></font>

688
00:59:34.946 --> 00:59:36.197
<font color="white">Hands on your head and surrender!</font><font color="white"></font>

689
00:59:41.786 --> 00:59:42.704
<font color="white">Uncle.</font><font color="white"></font>

690
00:59:44.080 --> 00:59:46.666
<font color="white">Damn it. always a little late.</font><font color="white"></font>

691
00:59:48.126 --> 00:59:49.836
<font color="white">-Hey. Sung Han-soo.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Yeah?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

692
00:59:50.336 --> 00:59:53.631
<font color="white">Are you the gift</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">Kim said he'd have waiting for me?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

693
00:59:54.340 --> 00:59:57.218
<font color="white">Well. we prepared a gift too.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">What do you think?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

694
00:59:58.011 --> 00:59:59.345
<font color="white">Do you like it?</font><font color="white"></font>

695
01:00:02.473 --> 01:00:03.391
<font color="white">Uncle.</font><font color="white"></font>

696
01:00:04.350 --> 01:00:05.476
<font color="white">What now?</font><font color="white"></font>

697
01:00:09.439 --> 01:00:10.773
<font color="white">Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

698
01:00:10.857 --> 01:00:14.485
<font color="white">If you look to your left behind you.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">you'll see an emergency exit.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

699
01:00:15.612 --> 01:00:16.946
<font color="white">On the count of three.</font><font color="white"></font>

700
01:00:17.655 --> 01:00:20.825
<font color="white">I need you to run that way</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">as fast as you can and don't look back.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

701
01:00:21.492 --> 01:00:22.785
<font color="white">What are you talking about?</font><font color="white"></font>

702
01:00:23.453 --> 01:00:25.455
<font color="white">-What about you?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Me?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

703
01:00:26.414 --> 01:00:29.834
<font color="white">I'm just going to say hi to those men</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">and then catch up with you.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

704
01:00:31.294 --> 01:00:33.254
<font color="white">You can't do this alone.</font><font color="white"></font>

705
01:00:33.338 --> 01:00:34.422
<font color="white">All right. One…</font><font color="white"></font>

706
01:00:35.715 --> 01:00:37.675
<font color="white">You can shoot Sung Han-soo</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">and claim it was an accident.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

707
01:00:37.759 --> 01:00:38.885
<font color="white">Don't kill the girl.</font><font color="white"></font>

708
01:00:38.968 --> 01:00:40.011
<font color="white">Two…</font><font color="white"></font>

709
01:00:40.094 --> 01:00:41.054
<font color="white">Uncle!</font><font color="white"></font>

710
01:00:51.230 --> 01:00:52.857
<font color="white">Fire!</font><font color="white"></font>

711
01:00:52.940 --> 01:00:53.941
<font color="white">Three.</font><font color="white"></font>

712
01:01:02.075 --> 01:01:03.117
<font color="white">What the hell was that?!</font><font color="white"></font>

713
01:01:06.954 --> 01:01:08.623
<font color="white">He's always late.</font><font color="white"></font>

714
01:01:10.917 --> 01:01:12.085
<font color="white">Flashbang.</font><font color="white"></font>

715
01:01:16.631 --> 01:01:17.465
<font color="white">Smoke grenade.</font><font color="white"></font>

716
01:01:30.061 --> 01:01:30.895
<font color="white">Attack.</font><font color="white"></font>

717
01:01:50.790 --> 01:01:51.708
<font color="white">Tactical team!</font><font color="white"></font>

718
01:01:52.458 --> 01:01:54.335
<font color="white">Rally at Zone C bunker!</font><font color="white"></font>

719
01:02:05.263 --> 01:02:06.180
<font color="white">Hey. get in!</font><font color="white"></font>

720
01:02:06.264 --> 01:02:08.599
<font color="white">Nice of you to finally show up.</font><font color="white"></font>

721
01:02:08.683 --> 01:02:10.184
<font color="white">It's okay. Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

722
01:02:21.154 --> 01:02:23.072
<font color="white">Why aren't you getting in? Hurry up!</font><font color="white"></font>

723
01:02:23.698 --> 01:02:26.033
<font color="white">How can we get in if the doors won't open?</font><font color="white"></font>

724
01:02:26.117 --> 01:02:27.577
<font color="white">What are we going to do?</font><font color="white"></font>

725
01:02:38.004 --> 01:02:39.505
<font color="white">Damn it.</font><font color="white"></font>

726
01:02:41.591 --> 01:02:42.759
<font color="white">You're shooting blanks. aren't you?</font><font color="white"></font>

727
01:02:47.889 --> 01:02:48.931
<font color="white">They're blank rounds.</font><font color="white"></font>

728
01:02:50.892 --> 01:02:51.851
<font color="white">Hey. take cover!</font><font color="white"></font>

729
01:02:53.561 --> 01:02:54.645
<font color="white">They're blank rounds! Fire!</font><font color="white"></font>

730
01:02:56.272 --> 01:02:57.398
<font color="white">Hey. Min-ji!</font><font color="white"></font>

731
01:02:58.524 --> 01:03:01.235
<font color="white">Oh. for crying out loud! My car!</font><font color="white"></font>

732
01:03:03.696 --> 01:03:06.157
<font color="white">Hey. you should've brought some live ammo!</font><font color="white"></font>

733
01:03:06.240 --> 01:03:08.785
<font color="white">Why did you bring all blank rounds?</font><font color="white"></font>

734
01:03:08.868 --> 01:03:10.161
<font color="white">They caught on right away.</font><font color="white"></font>

735
01:03:10.244 --> 01:03:12.163
<font color="white">I did bring live ammo!</font><font color="white"></font>

736
01:03:12.246 --> 01:03:14.665
<font color="white">But I can't go around</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">killing my juniors. can I?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

737
01:03:18.127 --> 01:03:19.796
<font color="white">Jeez. my car. man!</font><font color="white"></font>

738
01:03:28.179 --> 01:03:29.347
<font color="white">This won't do. huh?</font><font color="white"></font>

739
01:03:30.223 --> 01:03:31.057
<font color="white">Here.</font><font color="white"></font>

740
01:03:33.100 --> 01:03:33.935
<font color="white">Choose one!</font><font color="white"></font>

741
01:03:35.061 --> 01:03:37.939
<font color="white">I can't choose</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">because I love both of them!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

742
01:03:38.022 --> 01:03:40.024
<font color="white">-Choose one.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-You want to have a shootout?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

743
01:03:42.068 --> 01:03:43.236
<font color="white">Hold your fire!</font><font color="white"></font>

744
01:03:55.331 --> 01:03:56.499
<font color="white">Hey. Park Jin-cheol.</font><font color="white"></font>

745
01:03:57.625 --> 01:03:58.459
<font color="white">Now what?</font><font color="white"></font>

746
01:03:59.126 --> 01:04:00.253
<font color="white">You want us to continue?</font><font color="white"></font>

747
01:04:12.014 --> 01:04:13.558
<font color="white">This is a white flag.</font><font color="white"></font>

748
01:04:13.641 --> 01:04:14.475
<font color="white">We surrender!</font><font color="white"></font>

749
01:04:15.184 --> 01:04:16.644
<font color="white">We're coming out. so don't shoot!</font><font color="white"></font>

750
01:04:18.855 --> 01:04:19.814
<font color="white">We're coming!</font><font color="white"></font>

751
01:04:21.399 --> 01:04:22.525
<font color="white">Nice and slow!</font><font color="white"></font>

752
01:04:23.609 --> 01:04:24.777
<font color="white">Slowly!</font><font color="white"></font>

753
01:04:24.861 --> 01:04:26.112
<font color="white">Slowly!</font><font color="white"></font>

754
01:04:26.696 --> 01:04:27.905
<font color="white">Why are there so many of you?</font><font color="white"></font>

755
01:04:28.531 --> 01:04:30.533
<font color="white">All of you just to catch the three of us?</font><font color="white"></font>

756
01:04:33.953 --> 01:04:36.789
<font color="white">I saved you from drowning.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">and you shoot live ammo?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

757
01:04:37.415 --> 01:04:39.166
<font color="white">There's a kid here too. you mole rat.</font><font color="white"></font>

758
01:04:39.250 --> 01:04:42.753
<font color="white">You return to your old stomping grounds</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">after all this time. wreck the place.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

759
01:04:42.837 --> 01:04:43.713
<font color="white">and expect me to sit back?</font><font color="white"></font>

760
01:04:44.630 --> 01:04:45.464
<font color="white">Take her.</font><font color="white"></font>

761
01:04:45.548 --> 01:04:46.674
<font color="white">-Yes. sir.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Yes. sir.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

762
01:04:48.384 --> 01:04:49.427
<font color="white">All of you!</font><font color="white"></font>

763
01:04:50.511 --> 01:04:51.387
<font color="white">Drop your guns!</font><font color="white"></font>

764
01:05:01.981 --> 01:05:02.940
<font color="white">What are you doing?</font><font color="white"></font>

765
01:05:04.233 --> 01:05:05.943
<font color="white">I said drop your guns!</font><font color="white"></font>

766
01:05:53.699 --> 01:05:54.784
<font color="white">Dad?</font><font color="white"></font>

767
01:06:06.671 --> 01:06:07.797
<font color="white">Dad!</font><font color="white"></font>

768
01:06:07.880 --> 01:06:08.881
<font color="white">Wait here.</font><font color="white"></font>

769
01:06:11.384 --> 01:06:12.218
<font color="white">Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

770
01:06:14.553 --> 01:06:15.638
<font color="white">I'm here.</font><font color="white"></font>

771
01:06:22.061 --> 01:06:23.229
<font color="white">Let's go home now.</font><font color="white"></font>

772
01:06:23.813 --> 01:06:24.814
<font color="white">Dad…</font><font color="white"></font>

773
01:07:08.149 --> 01:07:11.861
<font color="white">AGENT KIM REACTIVATED</font><font color="white"></font>

774
01:07:13.446 --> 01:07:15.740
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I'm here now. so don't worry.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

775
01:07:18.367 --> 01:07:20.369
{\an8}<font color="white">I'm going to witness the end myself.</font><font color="white"></font>

776
01:07:20.453 --> 01:07:22.329
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Just take a quick nap. hero!</i></font><font color="white"></font>

777
01:07:23.330 --> 01:07:26.042
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>An attempted cover-up and a kidnapping…</i></font><font color="white"></font>

778
01:07:26.125 --> 01:07:28.753
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>We should take this chance</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>to get rid of him first.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

779
01:07:28.836 --> 01:07:30.421
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I'm sure you weren't</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>in your right mind either.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

780
01:07:30.504 --> 01:07:31.839
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>trying to find your daughter.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

781
01:07:31.922 --> 01:07:35.176
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Today will be the last time</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>Agent Kim sees Min-ji.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

782
01:07:36.010 --> 01:07:37.094
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Dad!</i></font><font color="white"></font>

783
01:07:39.597 --> 01:07:41.265
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>For Min-ji's sake.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

784
01:07:41.348 --> 01:07:42.516
{\an8}<font color="white">I'm going to</font><font color="white"></font>

785
01:07:42.600 --> 01:07:43.726
{\an8}<font color="white">end you.</font><font color="white"></font>

786
01:07:45.978 --> 01:07:48.898
{\an8}<font color="white">Subtitle translation by: Jenny Kim</font><font color="white"></font>

